gain my concentration and Root it.<P>That's why I wonder if wizards would consider it.  I understand the CONCEPT of timing it between shots, but wouldn't you rather NEVER get interrupted?<P>I watched a wizard soloing at the MG fort try to get Root off like FIVE times without success, paying for it with half his life.  Finally he gave up and started casting nukes through the damage.  After we grouped up, I was in charge of Rooting.<P>The added bonus would be Gate, Yonder, and Evac TP's.  I know that it's a stretch to try it... just an idea.  But if our stun has a 1 sec casting time, I'm not going to bother... I'll just stun-root them if getting hit, and I'll take a 'chanter, cleric, or shaman with me for giants.<P>Quintius<BR>Gnomish KaBOOM Technician<BR>13th Trial of KaBOOM Tactics<P>
